         <abstract id="aspace_65dd9abf9a289b896ec20f7d9b64828a">Collection consists of printed items, photographs, and other ephemera related to puppetry and puppet companies including Yale Puppeteers, the Prague Puppet Theatre, Tony Sarg and others. Four Javanese puppets are also included in the collection.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <relatedmaterial id="aspace_b38ea3ff25996d9dedcf8aabd6c1fac5">
         <head>Associated Materials</head>
         <p>Published Czech puppet plays, donated with the Prague Puppet Theater material, are cataloged in Orbis, Yale's online catalog, as part of the Slavic and East European Collections.</p>  
      </relatedmaterial>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_4007b1b1a7d0666fdff1637574ef5def">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>Gifts of numerous individuals to the Drama Library. Prague Puppet Theater Material donated by Vio Mae Powell in 1971.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_f709300a78d8db2bffddcbc1592d22a2">
