      <prefercite id="aspace_4be3e7f61a9b633c712fd52106f1c438">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Puppetry Collection, Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library, Yale University.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_5a70e641b228e1d30a88a53dfe1eae6b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Collection consists of printed items, photographs, and other ephemera related to puppetry and puppet companies including Yale Puppeteers, the Prague Puppet Theatre, Tony Sarg and others. Four Javanese puppets are also included in the collection.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_1084af9673223480e3b3236cee80137e">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged alphabetically by name of puppeteer or puppet theater.</p>  
      </arrangement>
